Builder's Guides ChangeLog
==========================

1.7.10-1.0.0

* Actual release of V1.0.0
** This means that, as per tradition, V1.0.1 will follow quickly
* Update to latest recommended Forge 10.13.2.1230
* com.ipsis.buildersguides -> ipsis.buildersguides
* Toned down the textures a bit

1.7.10-1.0.0B4

Fixes
* BGZ003 - Chunk marker was based off the players position not the marker block.

1.7.10-1.0.0B3

* Added the center marker than finds the centers between walls, rather than the marker and the target block.
* Added a toolbox to carry the markers. Doesn't hold general items.

Fixes
* BGZ001 - Fix the Multi-Range Marker display name
* BGZ002 - Breaking blocks by hand now drop the block

1.7.10-1.0.0B2

* Fix the modid and associated package, mod name.
* Update to latest forge 10.13.0.1189
* Add configuration file - only has one setting just now and that is to disable the guide lines rendering.

1.7.10-1.0.0B1

* Initial release